snippet.title: THE NOTHING | Small pre-alpha city demo
snippet.description:
(WATCH IN HD)

A tiny demo of the city. Nothing exciting, just people watching, stepping out in front of flying cars, purposely getting fined, stealing money, getting something to eat and smashing some wood with a sweet roundhouse.

Much more to come
